 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">One of the tensions in the cl=
imate fight is that we need to build more housing and other new buildings, =
but the construction and operation of buildings emits a lot of carbon. The =
real estate industry is responsible for 38% of greenhouse gas emissions glo=
